<AbstractNarration>Building Capacity Among Junior Researchers in the Learning Sciences: A Request for Special Program Support for the International Conference of the Learning Sciences: 2000&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;This is a SGER proposal to support graduate students to attend the International Conference on the Learning Sciences to be held in Ann Arbor June 14-17, 2000.  The funds would support the development of 3 workshops on methodology, would support junior faculty attending the meeting, and would provide support for graduate students to attend at a reduced price.  Also, the conference will hold a consortium for graduate student research at which students would present summaries of their research in process and receive comments from nationally recognized faculty.  &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;</AbstractNarration>
